      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a limited-slip variable M differential for optimal corner-exit traction. This example has undergone preventative maintenance on the dual-VANOS system and rear subframe mounting points. The suspension retains its factory-tuned balance with MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup, offering sharp turn-in and high-speed stability. A driver-focused machine in solid mechanical health.",
